patthana16.91:1.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ pariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paccayā nasanidassanasappaṭigho napariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.91:2.1_0: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca naanidassanaappaṭigho naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā.
patthana16.91:2.1_1: Anidassanaappaṭighaṁ apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho naapariyāpanno dhammo uppajjati hetupaccayā …pe… anidassanaappaṭighaṁ apariyāpannaṁ dhammaṁ paṭicca nasanidassanasappaṭigho naapariyāpanno ca naanidassanasappaṭigho naapariyāpanno ca dhammā uppajjanti hetupaccayā.
patthana16.91:2.1_2: (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā cha, adhipatiyā cha …pe… avigate cha.
